<plot>A horseman is courting the woman he loves while he leads his horse along. When he leaves her for a moment to tie the horse to a tree, a second man rides up in a motorcar, and begins to court the same woman. The two men have words with each other, but before they come to blows, the woman offers a challenge: she will give a kiss to the winner of a race between the horse and the automobile.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?015104</url></doc>
